#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.invert.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.invert"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:1 of
msgid "Compute bit-wise inversion, or bit-wise NOT, element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算按位取反，或按位 NOT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:3 of
msgid ""
"Computes the bit-wise NOT of the underlying binary representation of the "
"integers in the input tensors. This ufunc implements the C/Python "
"operator ``~``."
msgstr ""
"计算输入张量中整数的二进制表示的按位 NOT。此 ufunc 实现了 C/Python 运算符"
" ``~``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For signed integer inputs, the two's complement is returned.  In a "
"two's-complement system negative numbers are represented by the two's "
"complement of the absolute value. This is the most common method of "
"representing signed integers on computers [1]_. A N-bit two's-complement "
"system can represent every integer in the range :math:`-2^{N-1}` to "
":math:`+2^{N-1}-1`."
msgstr ""
"对于有符号整数输入，返回其二进制补码。在二进制补码系统中，负数由其绝对值"
"的二进制补码表示。这是计算机中表示有符号整数的最常用方法 [1]_。一个 N 位"
"的二进制补码系统可以表示范围为 :math:`-2^{N-1}` 到 :math:`+2^{N-1}-1` 的"
"所有整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:14 of
msgid "Only integer and boolean types are handled."
msgstr "仅处理整数和布尔类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:16 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:21 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:26 of
msgid "**out** -- Result."
msgstr "**out** -- 结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.invert.invert:29 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`bitwise_and`, :py:obj:`bitwise_or`, :py:obj:`bitwise_xor`, "
":py:obj:`logical_not`"
msgstr ""

